== Umwuga ==
Rugwizangoga ni umwanditsi wumwuga mu Rwanda, yabaye umusizi wegukanye ibihembo byinshi, umuhanzi wamagambo, umuhanga muguhanga. Yandika kandi akora ibitaramo mu Gifaransa, Icyongereza, Ikidage, Icyesipanyoli, ni Kinyarwanda, kandi asangira imivugo ye ku byiciro byinshi ku isi (muri Kigali, Kaiserslautern, Paris, Berlin, n'ahandi). Yashinze ikitwa "Words of the World (WOTW) akaba ari urubuga rufunguye rw'imivugo ruherereye mu Budage no mu Rwanda. .<ref>https://www.weforum.org/people/michaella-rugwizangoga</ref>
